	(text "Level shift 1.8V → 3.3V using NPN open-collector.\nTXD low → transistor saturates → MCU_RX pulled low.\nTXD high → transistor off → MCU_RX pulled up to 3.3V."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 131.064 41.402 0)
